with the warsaw pact as of nov 1 there were 213 million men and 
women in the armed services 
the services have drafted plans for a reduction of 275000 with 
about 135000 to be trimmed from the army 100000 from the air 
force and 40000 from the navy and marines defense sources told 
the associated press 
