weapons procurement for the army and air force according to a 
report in wednesdays editions of the washington post a final 
decision has not been made but members of congress have complained 
that the cuts are aimed mainly at workers and fieldlevel positions 
while not reducing the ranks of management 
bush said it was very important for the allies to know im not 
going to go off and prematurely jump out there and try to 
grandstand by committing them to something thats not the way you 
keep an alliance strong 
