mikhail gorbachev wants assurances from president 
bush this weekend that the united states will not exploit the 
eastern european reform movement say government officials who add 
the soviet leader hopes for improved trade ties from the superpower 
summit 
gorbachev also will be seeking progress on an array of arms 
