10000 to kill johnsons wife sharon according to an account of 
a police interview on monday filed with merrimack district court by 
state police sgt roland lamy 
pfaaf said he recruited jason carroll 19 to help kill her the 
night of july 28 1988 
johnson 37 currently of warwick ri pfaaf of wallace nc 
and formerly of manchester and carroll of new boston were all 
charged with capital murder tuesday in the womans death 
sharon johnson 36 was seven months pregnant and had been 
married to johnson for three years when she was killed 
