farberware endicott johnson and frye footwear universal gym gold 
fields mining and minority interests in smithcorona typewriters 
and newmont mining british properties include imperial tobacco and 
consolidated gold fields which it acquired earlier this year for 
57 billion britains largest takeover ever 
dollar figures for the 1989 and 1988 periods were converted from 
british pounds at the sept 30 rate of 1615 to the pound 
